rchive.is/20131104104412/http://www.canada.com/story_print.html?id=03978317-3343-471e-bda1-9b1a059003e9&sponsor=|url-status=dead|archive-date=2013-11-04|title=Fox takes chances with Fringe, Dollhouse|date=2008-07-14|accessdate=2013-11-03}}</ref>\n* ''[[Exile (TV series)|Exile]]''<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8489426/Exile-BBC-One-final-episode-preview.html|title=Exile, BBC One, final episode, preview|work=[[Daily Telegraph]]|date=2011-05-03|accessdate=2013-11-03}}</ref>\n* ''[[The Following]]''<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/the-following-natalie-zea-claire-414083|title='The Following': Natalie Zea Previews Fox's Psychological Thriller From Kevin Williamson|last=Ng|first=Philiana|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2013-01-21|accessdate=2013-11-03}}</ref>\n* ''[[Hannibal (TV series)|Hannibal]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://journalstar.com/entertainment/tv-radio/jeff-korbelik-hannibal-a-taut-psychological-thriller/article_88e737b2-2093-58a3-b14c-f1a103805ef9.html |title=Jeff Korbelik: 'Hannibal' a taut psychological thriller &#124; Television and radio |publisher=journalstar.com |date= |accessdate=2017-04-08}}</ref>\n* ''[[Homeland (TV series)|Homeland]]''<ref>{{cite news | first=Gary | last=Levin | title=At heart of 'Homeland' is a psychological thriller | url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/LIFE/usaedition/2011-09-29-Homeland-feature--_ST_U.htm | work=[[USA Today]] | date=2011-09-29 |accessdate=2013-11-03}}</ref>\n* ''[[Death Note (2015 TV series)|Death Note]]''\n* ''[[Jessica Jones (TV series)|Jessica Jones]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etonline.com/news/176457_everything_you_need_to_know_about_marvel_jessica_jones/|title=Everything You Need to Know Before Binge-Watching Marvel and Netflix's 'Jessica Jones'|last=Boone|first=John|work=[[Entertainment Tonight]]|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2016-02-13}}</ref>\n* ''[[Lost (TV series)|Lost]]''\n* ''[[Mad Dogs (UK TV series)|Mad Dogs]]''<ref>{{cite